Package edu.aau.g404.protocol.udp

package edu.aau.g404.protocol.udp
Provides classes for handling UDP requests in the IoT system.

This package contains the UdpRequest class, which is designed for sending UDP packets to smart devices that support communication over the User Datagram Protocol (UDP). The UdpRequest class can be used to send state updates to devices in the form of serialized JSON payloads.
